so unscrupulously.

304
00:12:31,790 --> 00:12:32,870
I really don't know

305
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,080
what to say about you,

306
00:12:34,090 --> 00:12:36,270
a cheeky and shameless person.

307
00:12:37,750 --> 00:12:38,590
Mrs. Su,

308
00:12:39,270 --> 00:12:40,630
you remind me of someone

309
00:12:40,630 --> 00:12:41,790
called Zhang Ying.

310
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:44,030
Is it true that in your opinion,

311
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:46,600
as long as a person has no money
or family background,

312
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:49,750
whatever he does is his fault?

313
00:12:49,750 --> 00:12:50,680
It's good that you know.

314
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,200
Don't you daydream

315
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:54,320
about marrying a rich girl.

316
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:58,600
Then how can you be so sure

317
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,910
that I have neither of these?

318
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:04,840
You mean

319
00:13:04,900 --> 00:13:07,080
