324
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:30,800
Sister Wan'er,

325
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:32,870
I was hesitant to intervene,

326
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:35,390
but from now on,

327
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,440
I'm in charge

328
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:40,000
of your marriage.

329
00:13:45,550 --> 00:13:46,840
I'll only marry you.

330
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:51,720
I... I didn't mean that. I was just...

331
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:53,960
So this is how you deceive my daughter.

332
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,200
Fine,

333
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:57,630
I'll reveal your true colors

334
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:59,080
