338
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:07,750
If you can afford one of them,

339
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:10,000
I'll let you pursue Wan'er.

340
00:14:10,630 --> 00:14:12,320
Who can afford those three pieces?

341
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:13,670
Indeed.

342
00:14:13,750 --> 00:14:15,320
What kind of rich family

343
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,720
