344
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:18,870
Wouldn't that guy be a joke if he went?

345
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,520
Bragging too much
will eventually backfire.

346
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:21,350
So what?

347
00:14:21,550 --> 00:14:22,630
Now you don't dare?

348
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:24,120
He's lucky to get in the door.

349
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:25,360
